{
  "text": ". . . there is a very real chance of survival but we cannot be certain about the outcome'' (qualitative) . . . . Moreover, surrogate decision makers desire a discussion that includes QOL indicators in addition to survival estimates. [CITATION_1] Prognostic assessment should also include an introduction to outcomes other than mortality and, in this case scenario, ventilator independence:",
